<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Krems an der Donau und Stein an der Donau</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass die Bürger zu Nürnberg bereits mit Stefan Halbpfaff und Heinz Gewölbherr ausgerichtet sind, und bittet um Anweisung des Halbpfaff, die ausstehenden elfeinhalb Gulden zu bezahlen.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_265" id="132v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_265_r1l23">Dem <expan>Rıcht<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd dem ~ Rate </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_265_r1l24">ʒu krems vnd Stein </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_265_r1l26"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt . von <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>s</expan> mıtwoners ſtepfan </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_265_r1l29">halbpfaffen vnd ſeins gemeiners heincʒen <expan>gwelbh<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_265_line_1576663594627_7760"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab></add> etc . das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_265_r1l30">alles <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_265_r1l31">wir etwıeuıl <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> dıe dıe ſache antrıft . vmb <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> für </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_265_r1l33">vns beſant vnd 
<add><ab facs="#facs_265_r1l32">darumb </ab></add> verhoret <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Dabey dıe <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> ʒwen von der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_265_r1l34"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> Jr vns <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt ın gegenwürtıkeıt vor vns geweſt </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_266" id="133r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_266_r2l2">ſein . vnd dıe alle auf beıd ſeıten / <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vor vns bekant / daʒ dıe <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_266_r2l4">ʒwen gemeiner vmb all 
<add><ab facs="#facs_266_r2l3">vergangen </ab></add> ſache <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ır vns denn <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt . hıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_266_r2l5">bey vns ʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> gütlıch berıcht vnd geeynt <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> ſein alſo daʒ der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_266_r2l6"><expan>obg<ex>enante</ex></expan> halbpfaff . den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>auſrıchte<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd becʒaln ſol . <expan>aılıfthalb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_266_r2l7">on des <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>gwelbh<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ſcheden . Doch ſo <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> gwelb = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_266_r2l8"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> . von der <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> ſchuld <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> nıht ledıg <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> noch <expan>ſag<ex>en</ex></expan> . alſlank bıs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_266_r2l9">ſıe <expan>Jr<ex>er</ex></expan> ſchulde becʒalt <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> . Das <expan>v<ex>er</ex>künd<ex>en</ex></expan> wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> . Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_266_r2l10"><expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅch mıt fleıſſ . daʒ Jr mıt dem <expan>halbpfaff<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> wellet . daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_266_r2l11">er dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cʒıehen</expan> auſrıcht vnd vnklaghaft mache . Denn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_266_r2l12">wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> . etc . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>ſab<ex>at</ex>o</expan> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> mathıe <expan>app<ex>oſto</ex>lȷ</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_265" id="132v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Dem <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> und dem rate zu Krems und Stein </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> mitwoners Stepfan Halbpfaffen und seins
                        gemeiners Heinczen <expan>Gwelbh<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<add><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan></add> etc., das alles
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                                <expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en,</ex></expan> daz wir etwievil
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger,</ex></expan> die die sache antrift, umb
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan> für uns besant und <add>darumb</add> verhoret
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, dabey die
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> zwen, von der
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ir uns <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        habt, in gegenwürtikeit vor uns gewest <pb facs="#facs_266" id="133r"/>sein. Und die
                        alle auf beid seiten <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vor uns bekant, daz die
                                <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> zwen gemeiner umb all
                            <add>vergangen</add> sache, <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ir uns denn
                                <expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, hie bey uns zu
                                <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> gütlich bericht und geeynt
                                <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> sein, also daz der
                                <expan>obg<ex>enante</ex></expan> Halbpfaff den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ausrichte<ex>n</ex></expan> und beczaln sol
                                <expan>ailifthalb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> on des <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>Gwelbh<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> scheden. Doch so
                            <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> Gwelb<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von
                        der <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> schuld <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        niht ledig <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> noch
                        <expan>sag<ex>en</ex></expan>, alslank bis sie <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        schulde beczalt <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>. Das
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>künd<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewch
                        mit fleiss, daz ir mit dem <expan>Halbpfaff<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> wellet, daz er die
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cziehen</expan>
                        ausricht und unklaghaft mache. Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Mathie <expan>app<ex>osto</ex>li.</expan>
</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
